{"tid":671824,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"葵聯邨空中花園已經唔係公共空間？","createTime":"2018-05-20T12:35:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-23T08:42:39.000Z","uid":59298,"like":46,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"6ef22f19e68bff29696a82c25295f4699578f03e","tid":671824,"uid":59298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T12:35:57.000Z","msg":"小弟今日見咁好天，雖然好撚熱，就去搵地方影下相 - 葵盛西邨同葵聯邨，會一會佢個空中花園<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n出發之前做咗research, 葵聯邨嘅空中花園係公共空間，開放俾一般民眾嘅<br />\n「葵聯邨第二期，工程項目名稱葵盛圍公屋發展計劃......<span style=\"color: red;\">此通道及空中花園，為公共空間，免費開放予公眾使用，惠及附近居民。</span>」<br />\n<br />\n到差唔多六點半嘅時候，我到咗葵聯邨，同保安姐姐講我先登記，請求上去空中花園，再放低身份證。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n保安姐姐話要call控制室先，之後我等咗10分鐘，控制室話唔得。<span style=\"color: red;\">我去同控制室討論，貴屋邨嘅空中花園係公共空間，一般民眾係有權先登記後進入。<br />\n佢叫我聽日九點打俾佢老總同佢講。</span><br />\n最後我見到開始燒天，狗衝翻葵盛西邨搵位影<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔知係因為保安問題，定係人流少，會令到一個公共空間變成非公共空間。我地應唔應該捍衛應有嘅權利，定係唔好煩鳩佢地？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">如果已經確定唔係公共空間，細力屌唔該</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afec6fc22164bbe109f971ca698718fcea7a169e","tid":671824,"uid":81575,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T12:49:22.000Z","msg":"公共空間登咩記，即屌佢啦"},{"pid":"7e98ba86b4277cdc0e94d466d235e50257e9e6b6","tid":671824,"uid":54181,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T12:52:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ad40559ca6771e9eef5836dc9357f66577d7d67d","tid":671824,"uid":60529,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T13:06:10.000Z","msg":"公共空間做咩要登記<br />\n正如商場d 公共空間櫈都唔洗登記啦"},{"pid":"533f4bdbb4445a369d1733b534398a917750ea7e","tid":671824,"uid":59298,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T13:12:05.000Z","msg":"我係1823講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4c55e1110bd63d3b97b716c4e58736d191d3e03","tid":671824,"uid":59298,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T16:07:54.000Z","msg":"1823會開case<br />\n<br />\n遲早會收班懶撚皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d066a6ebc475a1d3a8cb7656f39ef4b2f3ec69e","tid":671824,"uid":22390,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T16:10:18.000Z","msg":"上網查下地契<br />\n查清楚影好相做證據<br />\n下次再去玩過啦"},{"pid":"c3f181383d7fede5bd992dab8b33a2a04fc9dde6","tid":671824,"uid":77461,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T16:26:16.000Z","msg":"空中花園屬於公共空間<br />\n但接駁到空中花園路線就係管理範圍 唔通飛上去？<br />\n<br />\n成橦都係房署 應該要打1823問下房署解釋係點"},{"pid":"3fcb4e1b1e981daede63bf736798545e484a88a6","tid":671824,"uid":59298,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"c3f181383d7fede5bd992dab8b33a2a04fc9dde6","tid":671824,"uid":77461,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T16:26:16.000Z","msg":"空中花園屬於公共空間<br />\n但接駁到空中花園路線就係管理範圍 唔通飛上去？<br />\n<br />\n成橦都係房署 應該要打1823問下房署解釋係點"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T02:42:41.000Z","msg":"係呀 好撚on9 要入民居搭𨋢先去到<br />\n<br />\n唔知設計師諗乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"381a80dc80e7a30e06f7f9b8693769073e13f3f8","tid":671824,"uid":39463,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"3fcb4e1b1e981daede63bf736798545e484a88a6","tid":671824,"uid":59298,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"c3f181383d7fede5bd992dab8b33a2a04fc9dde6","tid":671824,"uid":77461,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T16:26:16.000Z","msg":"空中花園屬於公共空間<br />\n但接駁到空中花園路線就係管理範圍 唔通飛上去？<br />\n<br />\n成橦都係房署 應該要打1823問下房署解釋係點"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T02:42:41.000Z","msg":"係呀 好撚on9 要入民居搭𨋢先去到<br />\n<br />\n唔知設計師諗乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\